		<h1 class="title">随难民迁徙：从希腊出发，路上兴起了围绕难民的生意 | 难民危机是怎么回事 六</h1>
	</div>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
				<span class="name">Anemona Hartocollis</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-10-05 13:00:00 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
